# Banking Application Requirements

## Overview
Text-based Java application for a school assignment that simulates a basic banking system.

## Core Features
1. Account Management
   - Support for 4 different accounts, each with unique account numbers
   - Display account balance

2. Transactions
   - Process deposits and withdrawals
   - Handle multiple transaction types in single interaction
   - Maintain transaction history

3. Data Storage
   - Store account data in local files
   - Store transaction history in local files
   - Store account numbers in local files

## Implementation Notes
- All transactions are virtual (text-based input/output only)
- No actual financial transactions will be processed
